text: Ayutovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Isyangulovsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 129 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Ayutovo
